diagram: {
  shape: sequence_diagram
  label: "첫 자동결제 실패"

  client: "웹 클라이언트"
  client.style.fill: "#e8f3ff"
  client.style.stroke: "#2457a6"
  server: "우리 서버"
  server.style.fill: "#eaf8f3"
  server.style.stroke: "#1c7c66"
  toss: "토스페이먼츠 서버"
  toss.style.fill: "#f1edff"
  toss.style.stroke: "#7b4bc4"

  client -> server: |md
구독 확정 요청

**POST /subscriptions/confirm**
| {
    style.stroke: "#1c7c66"
    style.font-color: "#334155"
    style.font-size: 18
    style.italic: false
  }
  server.note_2: "빌링키 발급 성공\nbillingKey 암호화 저장"
  server -> toss: |md
첫 자동결제 승인 요청

**POST /v1/billing/{billingKey}**
| {
    style.stroke: "#7b4bc4"
    style.font-color: "#334155"
    style.font-size: 18
    style.italic: false
  }
  toss -> server: |md
결제 실패 응답

CARD_DECLINED / EXCEED_MAX_AMOUNT / INSUFFICIENT_FUNDS
| {
    style.stroke: "#1c7c66"
    style.font-color: "#334155"
    style.font-size: 18
    style.italic: false
  }
  server.note_5: "구독 활성화하지 않음\nsubscription.status = payment_failed\ninvoice failed, payment failed 저장"
  server -> client: |md
결제 실패 응답

402 FIRST_PAYMENT_FAILED
| {
    style.stroke: "#2457a6"
    style.font-color: "#334155"
    style.font-size: 18
    style.italic: false
  }
}
